Entity Framework
    It is a ORM(Object Relational Mapper)
    It let you work with Database using c# classes instead of SQL queries

Why use Entity Framework Core?
  ❌ Without EF (ADO.NET)
      Write SQL manually
      Handle connections
      Map data yourself
      More boilerplate code
  ✅ With EF Core
      Less code
      Type-safe
      Easier maintenance
      Automatic migrations
LINQ support
✅ Faster development
✅ Cleaner code
✅ Less error-prone

